snippet.title: Warhammer Online Cinematic Trailer 2
snippet.description: This new cinematic for Warhammer Online: Age of Reckoning thrusts viewers into the heat of RvR as the forces of Order battle to stop the marauding hordes of Destruction from taking the capital city of Altdorf. Visit http://www.warhammeronline.com
